<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>
      My career goal is to become a professional backend developer with Ruby on Rails.
      My future goal is to become a leader backend, with the ability to manage and deploy software systems that meet
      customer needs.
      I will continue to learn and develop my skills in information technology, network systems, security, and project
      management to achieve my goal.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I 've written</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %> </a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I 've built</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %> </a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
